node.text:
Designed specifically for the angler who is serious about crankbait fishing, Lew’s is excited to announce the release of the 2022 XD Cranking Series. 

“You can feel the perfect harmony of backbone and load in this rod when you are making those long crankbait casts, even with a lighter lure,” - @markdavisbasspro, 35-year pro angling veteran and bonafide crankbait expert. “It’s just so well balanced, with the forgiving blend of glass and the strength of some of the best graphite out there.”

Hear more about the XD Cranking Series & all new products from @icastshow at the link in our bio.

#Lews #LewsFishing #fishing #icast #icast2021 #crankingrod #TeamLews

IGTV + YouTube Premiere
 
For @mark_zona_fishing producing fishing shows are the equivalent of fishing a tournament, but the entry fee and stakes are much higher. We go behind the scenes as he prepares to film three back-to-back episodes of Pro Team Journal on Lake St. Clair. See the passion, dedication, and grind that Mark Zona puts into every single show.

@greghackneyfishing goes back to his roots in Episode 4. Watch along as he takes us through why he chose the career path of being a professional angler and what it takes to succeed at this level.

Together with Wally Marshall, one of fishing’s most popular crappie anglers of all time, Lew’s is pleased to introduce the Wally Marshall “Original” Classic Rod Series.

First class rod engineering is the standout feature of the Wally Marshall Classic rods. The premium IM8 blanks, designed to provide the perfect balance of backbone with a light, fast tip, deliver an astoundingly sensitive rod with plenty of strength to drag big slabs out of the deepest cover.  The rods feature stainless steel guides and inserts for maximum reliability, as well as lightweight graphite reel seats for added sensitivity

See full details & check out all the 2022 new products debuted at @icastshow at the link in our bio.

NEW for 2022 🚨

Team Lew’s is pleased to announce the NEW HyperMag Speed Spin. What sets the HyperMag Speed Spin apart is the extraordinary engineering of the lightweight magnesium body and the high strength magnesium skeletal rotor making it one of the lightest weight high performance spinning reels of the class.

Key to the development of the HyperMag Speed Spin is one of the newest members of the Lew’s Pro Team, @mark_zona_fishing. “I fish a lot of places that torture my spinning reels. The new HyperMag has stood up in a BIG way,” the Michigan native said. “The HyperMag Speed Spin drag system has been rock solid and frankly the feature that is hardest to accomplish in a spinning reel, is an exceptional drag system. Team Lew’s nailed it with the HyperMag.” 

HyperMag fans have come to expect only the best in reel performance: dependability. strength. The finest components engineered at the lightest weight. 

#Lews #icast #LewsFishing #HyperMagSpin #spinningreel #fishing #bassfishing #Zona
